Package: songscraper
Type: Package
Title: Scrape All Lyrics by an Artist from AZLyrics.com
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Aman Bhargava <amanbhargava2001@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Aman Bhargava <amanbhargava2001@gmail.com>
Description: A clean function that takes the name of an artist and scrapes all songs, lyrics, 
    album and year details from AZLyrics.com into a clean dataframe. This can be used for
    text-mining or whatever you wish.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr, tidyverse, rvest, magrittr
